       -b  Local port to bind for the listening connection (default port is 8080).

       -c  Maximum number of connections handled (10 by default).

       -d  Destination host to connect to.

       -i  Maximum number of ip numbers used in the pool (default is 1).

       -p  Remote tcp port to connect to (default port is 25).

       -s  Source ip address to be used (first ip in the pool).

